OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy in the evening with occasional
OL,7,Fbursts of showery rain, with just a
OL,8,Ffew clearer interludes, Some drier and
OL,9,Fclearer spells developing overnight.
OL,10,FPerhaps some coastal haar over
OL,11,FCaithness and Sutherland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother day of bright spells
OL,14,Fand scattered showers, some of these
OL,15,Fturning out quite heavy especially
OL,16,Fover East Highland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
