OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,6,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,7,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,8,FSaturday, turning heavy in west. Sunny
OL,9,Fspells and occasional rain on Sunday.
OL,10,FOccasionally windy weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
